The special nipple brush is designed with special round bristles on the tip that help clean the bulb part of the nipple thoroughly.

Stainless steel wire firmly binds the bristles of the bottle and nipple brush preventing the bristles from falling and ensuring maximum hygiene. This practical bottle and nipple brush from Farlin is suitable for washing other baby articles as well as a variety of household items.
